net.alantea.proper

Class ActionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.alantea.proper.ActionManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PropertyContainer

    public class ActionManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class ActionManager manages named action by calling methods in associated elements that manage the named action. Methods with zero or one parameter in action manager or element class may be extended with one or more @Manage annotations : Manage("action key string").
